Captain of Industry Game Code carve-out
=======================================

This repository may contain short excerpts of, or references to, Captain of
Industry game code -- including type names, method signatures, field names,
and small code samples -- most notably in `template/MODDING-REFERENCE.md`.

Any such Game Code is the property of MaFi Games and is included solely under
the terms of the Captain of Industry Modding Policy
(https://www.captain-of-industry.com/modding-policy). The MIT License above
applies only to this template's own original code and documentation, and does
NOT grant any rights to MaFi Games' Game Code.
